    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Features Section -->
<section id="features" class="py-24 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">你的数字 CTO 能做什么？</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-secondary max-w-2xl mx-auto">不只是写代码——而是像一个真正的技术合伙人一样思考和工作</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

      <!-- Feature 1 -->
      <div class="card p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <%= lucide_icon "code-2", class: "w-6 h-6 text-primary" %>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">全栈开发能力</h3>
        <p class="text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">从数据库设计到前端界面，从 API 到部署，全程自主完成。Rails、React、Python 都不在话下。</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 2 -->
      <div class="card p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-secondary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <%= lucide_icon "message-circle", class: "w-6 h-6 text-secondary" %>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">飞书 / 企微直接对话</h3>
        <p class="text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">不用装任何软件，直接在飞书或企业微信给 AI 发消息，它就能帮你改代码、查问题。</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 3 -->
      <div class="card p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-success/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <%= lucide_icon "brain", class: "w-6 h-6 text-success" %>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">长期记忆 · 懂你项目</h3>
        <p class="text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">记住你的技术选型、业务背景、代码风格。下次对话不用重复解释，直接干活。</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 4 -->
      <div class="card p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-info/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <%= lucide_icon "clock", class: "w-6 h-6 text-info" %>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">定时自动执行任务</h3>
        <p class="text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">设定定时任务，让 AI 每天自动跑数据分析、生成报告、清理垃圾数据，你睡觉它干活。</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 5 -->
      <div class="card p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-warning/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <%= lucide_icon "shield-check", class: "w-6 h-6 text-warning" %>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">本地部署 · 数据不出境</h3>
        <p class="text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">代码和数据完全跑在你本地，不上传任何服务器。企业级数据安全，放心用。</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 6 -->
      <div class="card p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-danger/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <%= lucide_icon "layers", class: "w-6 h-6 text-danger" %>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">技能扩展 · 无限可能</h3>
        <p class="text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">通过自定义 Skill，给 AI 安装新能力。一键部署、自动测试、生成文档……随你定制。</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- How it works -->
