    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-primary flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-2xl font-black shadow-md" style="color: hsl(0 0% 100%)">1</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">安装大胜龙虾</h3>
        <p class="text-secondary text-sm">一行命令安装到你电脑，2分钟完成配置。支持 Mac / Windows / Linux。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-primary flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-2xl font-black shadow-md" style="color: hsl(0 0% 100%)">2</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">连接你的 IM / 浏览器</h3>
        <p class="text-secondary text-sm">绑定飞书或企微，或直接用浏览器访问 AI 工作台，随时随地开聊。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-primary flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-2xl font-black shadow-md" style="color: hsl(0 0% 100%)">3</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">说需求，等交付</h3>
        <p class="text-secondary text-sm">用中文描述你想做什么，AI 自主规划、写代码、测试、部署，你只负责验收。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

